\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\fs20 Domain:}{\fs20  The fists have their base of operations in the huge city of Cora\rquote Lyst on the
 southern coast. They are a powerful clan, and their dominion stretches for a fair distance in all directions, except of course south. Powerful in military terms they are also powerful when it comes to trade, the highway linking Cora\rquote Lyst to Cora
\rquote Tyl and sea trade along the coast and up the river Tzan to Il\rquote Cora\rquote 
