pon the seas not something that happens. Their patrols go as far as Falsta Tandar along the highway to Cora\rquote Tyl. 
\par }\pard\plain \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang3081\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp3081\langfenp1033 {\b\f38\cf2\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 [Mark: Navy\'85
